name: North Georgia Health
tweet: Everyone age 18+ is eligible for a COVID-19 booster.  If you got an mRNA vaccine, Pfizer or Moderna, get a booster 6 months after fully vaccinated.  If you got a one-dose vaccine, Johnson & Johnson/Janssen, get a booster 2 months after vaccination.  More:  https://t.co/rKQ85sMrPl  https://t.co/9CGGCYKuBY
